Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.35,0:00:20.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.76,0:00:22.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.87,0:00:29.90,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.24,0:00:40.56,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,We've left the established course
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.56,0:00:43.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we're rowing straight toward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.98,0:00:49.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The borderline between the sky and the ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.52,0:00:55.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,In the dark depths of the ocean,\Nadventure holds its breath
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.74,0:01:02.75,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a good time just imagining it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.75,0:01:07.25,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.25,0:01:09.33,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.33,0:01:16.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.58,0:01:27.03,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"That feeling" I get when embarking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.03,0:01:30.23,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something I hope to remember always
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.23,0:01:35.78,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can, I won't be afraid of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.78,0:01:41.99,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,With our pulses racing, let's go on a trip now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.99,0:01:49.04,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Shy hearts engrave the rhythm of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.04,0:01:53.17,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.17,0:01:55.79,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.79,0:02:00.15,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.15,0:02:02.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.85,0:02:04.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Life is "Adventurous"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.52,0:02:06.23,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Be aware it's "Dangerous"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.23,0:02:07.89,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna be "One of us"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.89,0:02:09.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And a trip goes on because
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:11.06,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,We da pirate of the "Mass"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.06,0:02:12.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,To the West, To the East
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.98,0:02:14.59,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta find my way, Sail away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.59,0:02:15.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,All the way to "One piece"!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.76,0:02:20.02,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff a dream into your empty chest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.02,0:02:22.20,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And spread your wings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.20,0:02:26.58,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If the wind blowing through\Nthem dyes your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.58,0:02:29.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's press forward
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.00,0:02:33.11,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.11,0:02:35.49,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.49,0:02:39.90,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.90,0:02:43.01,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.81,0:02:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.04,0:02:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.75,0:02:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.86,0:02:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.21,0:03:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.30,0:03:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.38,0:03:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.34,0:03:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.41,0:03:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.36,0:03:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This shadow will bring me one step closer
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.95,0:03:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to becoming the King of the Pirates, Hogback!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.28,0:03:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a decade since we first met.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.69,0:03:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I put all of my prowess into creating\NNo. 900 for a day such as this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.28,0:03:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With that shadow in it,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.76,0:03:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm certain it'll become the\Nmost powerful zombie in history!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.94,0:03:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will be a great asset!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.78,0:03:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The day I become the world's\N"King of the Grave" is close at hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.09,0:03:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can practically see the day I turn\Nthe cute critters of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.53,0:04:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,into zombies and make them\Nserve me in my dream kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.22,0:04:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heave, ho! Heave, ho! Heave, ho!\NHeave, ho! Heave, ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.59,0:04:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Luffy!\N--Stupid! Don't pop out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.95,0:04:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He won't die just because they took his shadow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.58,0:04:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.21,0:04:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.39,0:04:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, guys, take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.89,0:04:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.83,0:04:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The zombies' weakness!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.49,0:04:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is their weakness? What exactly is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.42,0:04:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's salt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.62,0:04:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To reiterate, please stuff salt into\Na zombie's mouth to defeat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.58,0:04:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the trick! Even for this\Nbag of bones, that's a snap!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.18,0:04:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Snap! Snap! Snap!\N--But Brook...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.26,0:04:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so knowledgeable\Nabout the zombies and this island?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.88,0:04:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That has to do with when I lost\Nmy shadow five years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.72,0:04:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally, they sent me back out to drift at sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.27,0:04:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fortunately, I was able to\Nturn back by the time I awoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.15,0:05:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And thus I returned to the island and fought.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.86,0:05:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But in the end, I lost miserably.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.22,0:05:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you'll have to pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.73,0:05:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in a hurry. Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.85,0:05:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.12,0:05:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of everything you've told us,\Nanswer this one question before you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.55,0:05:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.68,0:05:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I saw his corpse in the Land of Ice,\Nmy body wouldn't stop trembling.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.89,0:05:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had never dreamed I'd get to see\Nthat legend with my own two eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.44,0:05:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a zombie creator's--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.40,0:05:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Cindry-chan! Why are\Nyou walking in front of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.90,0:05:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet another legend shall come back to life!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.86,0:05:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see, No. 900.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.99,0:06:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, it's time for him to awaken!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.93,0:06:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is the only berserker to have\Ngone down in history as a "Devil."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.33,0:06:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oars!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.12,0:06:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Awakening After 500 Years!!\NOars Opens His Eyes!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.74,0:07:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get this underway!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.93,0:07:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that? A-A giant's... corpse?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.34,0:07:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even for a giant, it's freaking huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.27,0:07:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make a sound, Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.11,0:07:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be still, Straw Hat Luffy's shadow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.04,0:08:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am your new master.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.34,0:08:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm about to provide you with a voice and body
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.49,0:08:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so that you may live as a zombie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.80,0:08:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget all of your past relations\Nand become my obedient soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.41,0:08:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.39,0:08:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.02,0:08:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should have made Cindry-chan\Nagree to forget her past, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.94,0:08:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'd actually get to eat on plates.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.03,0:08:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could break your knee caps like plates.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.99,0:08:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yikes! Cindry-chan, that threat was super scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.74,0:08:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cindry doesn't show Hogback\Nany mercy, does she?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.03,0:08:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a Hog-smackdown...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.36,0:08:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.92,0:08:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time! Awaken!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.29,0:09:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Luffy's shadow...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.01,0:09:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arise from 500 years of slumber!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.40,0:09:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.96,0:09:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy's shadow...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.77,0:09:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It went in!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.28,0:11:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Don't scream!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.83,0:12:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The corpse moved!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.34,0:12:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.29,0:12:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-C-Crap! They found us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.01,0:12:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I screamed out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.37,0:12:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A demon has awoken!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.66,0:12:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kumacy! Don't tell me\Nyou've been sheltering the pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.84,0:12:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My bride! What are you doing down here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.85,0:12:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't let you escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.68,0:13:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magnificent!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.88,0:13:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How truly overawing!\NHe's a piece of art! A real devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.08,0:13:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.19,0:13:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.80,0:13:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.30,0:13:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kumacy, don't let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.03,0:14:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Okay!\N--What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.91,0:14:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Now zoom!\N--Yep!\N--Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.25,0:14:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Where are the pirates?\NWhere did my bride go?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.76,0:14:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They ran as fast as their legs could carry them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.26,0:14:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, can they run!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.57,0:14:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tch! I won't let them escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.93,0:14:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji, feed me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.36,0:14:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Sanji? Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.22,0:15:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that? What did we just witness?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.21,0:15:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The corpse started to move\Nafter he inserted Luffy's shadow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.01,0:15:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the deal behind these zombies.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.39,0:15:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is how Dr. Hogback\Nbrings people back to life...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.42,0:15:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That huge creep's ability probably stems from...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.64,0:15:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a Devil Fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.10,0:15:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Considering the first word out\Nof his mouth was "meat"...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.39,0:15:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that monstrous giant clearly\Nhas Luffy's personality, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.13,0:15:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yeah...\N--Then think back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.11,0:15:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We ran into a penguin in the\Nbreezeway who resembled Sanji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.50,0:15:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't kick a woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.00,0:15:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...even if it kills me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.83,0:15:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! So does that mean\Nhe had Sanji's shadow?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.45,0:15:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it does!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.16,0:15:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was the samurai who hit\Nus with the back of his sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.97,0:15:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May I see your panties?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.43,0:15:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.89,0:16:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was Brook's shadow! And we had no idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.06,0:16:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of the strange things on this\Nisland are starting to make sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.86,0:16:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was just pretending to make zombies!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.51,0:16:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That man is making a mockery of human life!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.99,0:16:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is this fulfilling "mankind's dream"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.65,0:16:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is this "resurrecting the dead"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.46,0:16:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Hogback is a truly\Nwonderful man! I respect him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.59,0:16:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He isn't the least bit\Ninterested in saving people!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.09,0:16:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's just a scumbag!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.06,0:16:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.43,0:16:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have time to lament over that now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.06,0:16:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our pals fell victim to his\Ngame of make-believe zombies!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.44,0:16:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you see? We're the\Nonly ones who can save them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.11,0:16:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry! They carried\NLuffy's body down this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.53,0:16:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! The perv said to take him to the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.21,0:16:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he meant Sunny.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.78,0:17:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Zoro and Sanji met the same fate,\Nwe might find them there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.50,0:17:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear, those guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.10,0:17:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...can be such a handful!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.81,0:17:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp! Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.40,0:17:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.34,0:17:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?! Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.13,0:17:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.11,0:18:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This freak... is really strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.52,0:18:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Care to say your last farewells?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.57,0:18:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This woman is going to marry me today!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.56,0:18:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moron! If I can't protect a single woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.87,0:18:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...there was no point in being born a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.46,0:18:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Usopp, that weapon--!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.11,0:18:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why does Usopp have it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.62,0:18:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.95,0:18:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Six Chamber Viper Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.27,0:18:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's vanishing again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.78,0:18:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I'm disappearing too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.32,0:19:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.96,0:19:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami vanished with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.77,0:19:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.54,0:19:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.75,0:19:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.67,0:19:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some strong odor is masking his scent!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.42,0:19:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Save me, Usopp! Cho--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.38,0:19:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Nami! What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.24,0:19:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.68,0:19:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me, Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.55,0:19:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zombies, I'll let you take over from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.88,0:19:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Catch those two and bring\Nthem before Moria-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.90,0:19:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot! Which direction\Nis his voice coming from?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.66,0:19:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.36,0:19:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp, behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.04,0:19:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?! A zombie in armor?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.34,0:20:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bunch of zombies are downstairs, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.61,0:20:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.07,0:20:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, this looks bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.98,0:20:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got a bunch of zombies upstairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.27,0:20:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, pirates! Hand over your shadows!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.94,0:20:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ch-Chopper, don't get caught!\NThey'll take our shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.08,0:20:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.87,0:20:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shadows...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.67,0:20:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your shadows...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.33,0:20:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hand over your shadows!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.81,0:20:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is even a zombie painting!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.01,0:20:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.00,0:20:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! You guys play dirty!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.60,0:20:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're immortal and get to\Nattack in numbers! It's no fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.48,0:20:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's low! Aw, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.77,0:20:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All we want is your shadow, bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.48,0:21:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! Let go! Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.28,0:21:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't let them catch us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.76,0:21:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.07,0:21:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's more?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.55,0:21:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fork over your shadows!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.84,0:21:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.20,0:21:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give us your shadows!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.04,0:22:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grah! W-We... We're doomed...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.21,0:22:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.10,0:22:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, someone else is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.10,0:22:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our buddies are getting purified!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.32,0:22:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better get your mitts...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.83,0:22:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...off my sworn little brothers, punks!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.78,0:22:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Certainly!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.70,0:22:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the heck are those guys?\NThey're rottin' bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.81,0:22:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.72,0:23:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.74,0:23:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did we take too long? We're short one.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.84,0:23:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp, Chopper, are you two all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.54,0:23:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're my shadow,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.99,0:23:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,why don't you understand\Nhow important this afro is?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.33,0:23:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a reason why I can't afford to lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.54,0:23:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not my afro! Anything but the 'fro!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.43,0:23:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.01,0:23:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Belief Worth Begging to Live For!!\NBrook Defends His Afro!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.60,0:23:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
